Hello.

this is plinker.

packet_filter.py listens to traffic, analyzes it (a bit) and sends statistic information via OSC

ck/plinker is a chuck program that turns that information into sound


we use:
* chuck [http://chuck.cs.princeton.edu/]
* pcapy
* pyOSC
* scapy

video demonstration:
* http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CCzGKBQQIvA


originally developed for the audio vu [http://audiovu.piringer.net/] at tuwien

